BEGIN NOW His project meanwhile was very favourably entertained by his auditors and
won hearty eulogies from all though Mr Dixon of Mary's excepted to it,
asking with a finicking air did he purpose also to carry coals to
Newcastle. END
BEGIN NOW Mr Mulligan however made court to the scholarly by an apt
