BEGIN NOW MAIS BIEN SUR,
noble stranger, said he cheerily, ET MILLE COMPLIMENTS. END
BEGIN NOW That you may and
very opportunely. END
BEGIN NOW There wanted nothing but this cup to crown my felicity. END
BEGIN NOW But, gracious heaven, was I left with but a crust in my wallet and a
