BEGIN NOW I declare, I was never so touched in
all my life. END
BEGIN NOW God, I thank thee, as the Author of my days! END
BEGIN NOW Thrice happy
will he be whom so amiable a creature will bless with her favours. END
BEGIN NOW A sigh
of affection gave eloquence to these words and, having replaced the
