BEGIN NOW But indeed,
sir, I wander from the point. END
BEGIN NOW How mingled and imperfect are all our
sublunary joys. END
BEGIN NOW Maledicity! END
BEGIN NOW he exclaimed in anguish. END
BEGIN NOW Would to God that
foresight had but remembered me to take my cloak along! END
BEGIN NOW I could weep to
think of it. END
BEGIN NOW Then, though it had poured seven showers, we were neither of
