BEGIN NOW Pooh! END
BEGIN NOW A LIVRE! END
BEGIN NOW cries Monsieur Lynch. END
BEGIN NOW The clumsy things are
dear at a sou. END
BEGIN NOW One umbrella, were it no bigger than a fairy mushroom, is
