BEGIN NOW Strike me silly, said Costello, a low fellow who was fuddled. END
BEGIN NOW A
monstrous fine bit of cowflesh! END
BEGIN NOW I'll be sworn she has rendezvoused you. END
BEGIN NOW What, you dog? END
BEGIN NOW Have you a way with them? END
BEGIN NOW Gad's bud, immensely so, said Mr
Lynch. END
BEGIN NOW The bedside manner it is that they use in the Mater hospice. END
BEGIN NOW Demme, does not Doctor O'Gargle chuck the nuns there under the chin. END
BEGIN NOW As I
look to be saved I had it from my Kitty who has been wardmaid there any
