BEGIN NOW Drat the man! END
BEGIN NOW Bless me,
I'm all of a wibbly wobbly. END
BEGIN NOW Why, you're as bad as dear little Father
Cantekissem, that you are! END
BEGIN NOW May this pot of four half choke me, cried
Costello, if she aint in the family way. END
BEGIN NOW I knows a lady what's got a
white swelling quick as I claps eyes on her. END
BEGIN NOW The young surgeon, however,
rose and begged the company to excuse his retreat as the nurse had just
