BEGIN NOW On the vigil of the 15th anniversary
of her birth she wrote a letter from Mullingar, county Westmeath, making
a brief allusion to a local student (faculty and year not stated). END
BEGIN NOW Did that first division, portending a second division, afflict him? END
BEGIN NOW Less than he had imagined, more than he had hoped. END
BEGIN NOW What second departure was contemporaneously perceived by him similarly,
if differently? END
BEGIN NOW A temporary departure of his cat. END
BEGIN NOW Why similarly, why differently? END
BEGIN NOW Similarly, because actuated by a secret purpose the quest of a new male

(Mullingar student) or of a healing herb (valerian). END
BEGIN NOW Differently, because
of different possible returns to the inhabitants or to the habitation. END
BEGIN NOW In other respects were their differences similar? END
BEGIN NOW In passivity, in economy, in the instinct of tradition, in
unexpectedness. END
BEGIN NOW As? END
BEGIN NOW Inasmuch as leaning she sustained her blond hair for him to ribbon it for
her (cf neckarching cat). END
BEGIN NOW Moreover, on the free surface of the lake in
Stephen's green amid inverted reflections of trees her uncommented spit,
describing concentric circles of waterrings, indicated by the constancy
of its permanence the locus of a somnolent prostrate fish (cf
mousewatching cat). END
BEGIN NOW Again, in order to remember the date, combatants, issue and consequences
