BEGIN NOW What would be his civic functions and social status among the county
families and landed gentry? END
BEGIN NOW Arranged successively in ascending powers of hierarchical order, that of
gardener, groundsman, cultivator, breeder, and at the zenith of his
career, resident magistrate or justice of the peace with a family crest
